# Band 8 Sample Answer

## Introduction

The pie charts compare the purposes of passengers travelling from four airports in the UK in 2016, namely Gatwick, Heathrow, Luton and Stansted.

**翻译：**
这些饼图比较了2016年英国四个机场——盖特威克机场、希思罗机场、卢顿机场和斯坦斯特德机场——旅客出行目的的分布情况。

---

## Overview

Overall, holidays and visiting friends or relatives were the two main reasons for air travel across all four airports, whereas travelling for other purposes accounted for only a very small proportion. In addition, Gatwick had the highest percentage of holidaymakers, while Luton and Stansted recorded the largest shares of passengers visiting friends and family.

**翻译：**
总体来看，度假以及探亲访友是四个机场旅客出行的主要原因，而其他目的所占比例都非常小。此外，盖特威克机场的度假旅客比例最高，而卢顿机场和斯坦斯特德机场则拥有最大的探亲访友旅客比例。

---

## Body Paragraph 1

At Gatwick Airport, more than half of passengers travelled for holidays, at 54%, making it the dominant category. Visiting friends or family represented 30%, while only 14% flew for business purposes. Similarly, holiday travel was also the leading reason at Heathrow Airport, although the figure was considerably lower at 33%. In contrast, Heathrow recorded a much higher proportion of business travellers, at 28%, while 37% of passengers were visiting acquaintances or relatives.

**翻译：**
在盖特威克机场，超过一半的旅客是为了度假出行，占54%，成为最主要的类别。探亲访友旅客占30%，而商务出行仅占14%。类似地，度假也是希思罗机场旅客出行的主要原因，不过其比例明显较低，仅为33%。相比之下，希思罗机场的商务旅客比例高得多，达到28%，而37%的旅客是为了探亲访友。

---

## Body Paragraph 2

A different pattern can be seen at Luton and Stansted airports, where visiting friends and family was the most common purpose. The proportions stood at 50% and 48% respectively. Meanwhile, holiday travel accounted for 35% of passengers at Luton and 36% at Stansted, whereas business-related travel made up relatively modest shares of 13% and 14%. Notably, the percentage for other reasons was identical across all four airports, at only 2% to 4%.

**翻译：**
卢顿机场和斯坦斯特德机场则呈现出不同的模式，探亲访友是最常见的出行目的，其比例分别为50%和48%。与此同时，度假旅客在卢顿和斯坦斯特德分别占35%和36%，而商务出行所占比例相对较低，仅为13%和14%。值得注意的是，因其他原因出行的旅客在四个机场中比例都非常接近，仅为2%到4%。

---

# ⭐ Band 8 写法解析

## ✅ 这篇为什么像 Band 8？

因为它：

* 有明确 overview
* 做了分类比较
* 使用高级比较结构
* 避免机械报数字
* 数据整合自然

而不是：

❌ “Gatwick was 54%. Heathrow was 33%…”

---

# ⭐ 这题最关键的思路

很多学生会：

# 一个机场写一段

这样会显得：

* 逻辑松散
* 比较不足
* 很像流水账

真正高分：

# “按特点分类”

---

## 第一类：

Holiday 主导：

* Gatwick
* Heathrow

---

## 第二类：

Visiting friends/family 主导：

* Luton
* Stansted

这就是：

# IELTS Task 1 高级分类逻辑

---

# ⭐ 可以直接背的高级表达

## 表达“占主导”

> making it the dominant category

---

## 表达“明显更低”

> considerably lower

---

## 表达“不同模式”

> A different pattern can be seen...

非常典型 Band 8。

---

## 表达“相对较小比例”

> made up relatively modest shares

---

## 表达“比例相同”

> was identical across all four airports

---

# ⭐ 高分比较句

## 对比结构

> In contrast,...

---

## meanwhile 衔接

> Meanwhile,...

---

## whereas 对比

> whereas business-related travel...

这些是：

# Cohesion and Coherence 高分核心

---

# ⭐ 这类 multiple pie charts 最重要的事

不要：

❌ 一个图一个图写

而要：

# 找“共性”和“差异”

例如：

* 哪些机场 holiday 最多
* 哪些机场 business 高
* 哪些机场 visiting friends/family 更突出

这样文章会：

# 更像“数据分析”

而不是“数字翻译”。
